{"tid":430571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「夢撚」有冇人好怕發夢既場景","createTime":"2017-10-10T02:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T05:09:40.000Z","uid":126977,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7e55d3f319075be1d559e38eecea13bd4f9dd9","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:03:09.000Z","msg":"我愈黎愈怕發夢，<br />\n雖然夢入面既地方都係平時見過，但係係夢入面就比自己個腦將幾個9唔搭8既地方砌埋一齊，感覺就會好熟悉又好陌生<br />\n例如夢見自己係歐洲（但係見到既唔係歐洲，只係夢入面知道自己係歐洲），行過度門就去番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n夢入面見到既野又會同意識有矛盾，例如夢中既時間係凌晨3點，但係個場景係日出手咁光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者夢見你好熟既朋友，但係夢入面佢身份係個殺手，或者係個唔識你既路人，自己既意識就會覺得奇怪<br />\n<br />\n又有時夢到自己另一個世界觀既世界，完成唔到某件事就要死。醒番果下係覺得自己真係去左果個世界，真係死左先跌番黎'現實' （莊周夢蝶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n甚至試過夢番好現實既日常生活，但係入面既人全部唔同晒，結果我訓醒果陣認唔到身邊既人（好短時間，不過個人清醒番都覺得好驚訝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n愈黎愈怕發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcae1d0012ba410d32b45ea3014062d0d8ac1441","tid":430571,"uid":7419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:09:09.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦你"},{"pid":"116d01f63ccdcb5d5bea226931466fa5783603f3","tid":430571,"uid":69130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"成日跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520d3b6cf40ef5190bffb15adc1f77f2fb61e817","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇醫生啦你</blockquote><br />\n會係咩病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37f21df933dccfcf82020c934726c85187b8732","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738be5ebe0e50893a93eba30617240a16603239c","tid":430571,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:50:43.000Z","msg":"我都勁多夢<br />\n個要成日係啲恐怖蘿 多數比人追殺"},{"pid":"a9894a3b7e2a514571b74e53aaf6c2ec86a320ce","tid":430571,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係發見到人跳樓  仲要撻係我面前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17d99d4c5f889caf66111ae691ecce4b0e5d2de","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都勁多夢<br />\n個要成日係啲恐怖蘿 多數比人追殺</blockquote><br />\n仲攰過冇訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7488660743bc7e4a36204803167bb7cdbd788c","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係發見到人跳樓  仲要撻係我面前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪真實見過人跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16d7002c30efe8b608b2126b24e126faf2fb542","tid":430571,"uid":48663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"我發啲夢都好撚恐怖<br />\n<br />\n比人追殺，夢到自己跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又會發啲好不安既夢，跟住喊喊到醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e504e49ef4a07da987e9466cebe5b67954e3b0d1","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike