iggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3574499098243c1419a5e5a3bb64dad88f66a000","tid":430571,"uid":3947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:56:24.000Z","msg":"成日夢到自己係個好高既地方跌落去"},{"pid":"50af53ab408e7f28930b0f952a973597db779cfe","tid":430571,"uid":68040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"我都成日發同一個夢<br />\n<br />\n例如係大廈比唔知係人定鬼追殺緊<br />\n但落極樓梯<br />\n每一層都淨係見到個數字係4樓<br />\n好撚不安"},{"pid":"6119ace701378bdb270aa9a8b8f956952cebb45c","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正喎 我反而好鐘意發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗下 每次發夢都好似去左第二個世界咁<br />\n好似冒險<br />\n但係又唔會有生命危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你好正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就只係想有完美睡眠休息下 但係就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c258ce2a4cce90e330f01e4cf69ed6bee351c40f","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日夢到自己係個好高既地方跌落去</blockquote><br />\n之後會好染咁震醒左仲比其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ee0c974ccdec4ddfffe64f80e3aac514b69f90","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都成日發同一個夢<br />\n<br />\n例如係大廈比唔知係人定鬼追殺緊<br />\n但落極樓梯<br />\n每一層都淨係見到個數字係4樓<br />\n好撚不安</blockquote><br />\n好重無助感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我夢親搭𨋢都冇好野 永遠同一層 又係4/14樓"},{"pid":"017b793312e9edcaab4cbc0fe66b4137c7e05d00","tid":430571,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係發見到人跳樓  仲要撻係我面前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪真實見過人跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未呀就係<br />\n個夢都幾震撼 有人企喺工業大廈頂<br />\n我係對面街<br />\n個人向前行一步  個人就飛落街 <br />\n途中唔知撞到乜 身首異處<br />\n個身係對面行人路落地   <br />\n個頭就好似波咁落地彈起飛向我面前<br />\n啲血好似彩虹咁淺哂係我塊面同身到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a215924219c90c85dfdeb62809b3173580fb311b","tid":430571,"uid":133277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:15:02.000Z","msg":"成日發夢急尿要去廁所<br />\n但d廁所一係冇門 一係就勁污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd84257cfcb04d5c21068f5b87bc6fec01b31020","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係發見到人跳樓  仲要撻係我面前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪真實見過人跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未呀就係<br />\n個夢都幾震撼 有人企喺工業大廈頂<br />\n我係對面街<br />\n個人向前行一步  個人就飛落街 <br />\n途中唔知撞到乜 身首異處<br />\n個身係對面行人路落地   <br />\n個頭就好似波咁落地彈起飛向我面前<br />\n啲血好似彩虹咁淺哂係我塊面同身到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaece40174b6dd20c8486fe7b759d3ac194783b2","tid":430571,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日發夢急尿要去廁所<br />\n但d廁所一係冇門 一係就勁污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個發依d夢會真係瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666c4bfee731e34dc3f5c7192d210d8b6c705f99","tid":430571,"uid":55405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"成